Naho amazinga n'ibiyaga bininibinini biri hafi y'inkengera z'ibahari bishobora gukwirwamwo ubwato bw'ubwoko bwose, amato matomato mbere n'ubwato bwo mu bwoko bwa kajugujugu ni ikindi kintu.
Gukoresha ubwato ni uburyo bwo kwisamaza mu gihugu ca Finlande: umwe ku bantu indwi canke umunani b'abafinlande arafise ubwato.
Ariko naho biri uko, ni ibiharuro bidasanzwe (nk'akarorero mu Buholande, umuntu umwe kuri mirongo ine afise ubwato).
Ubwinshi bw'ubwato butandukanye bwo mu karere ka Baltique burimwo n'uburaro i Saint-Pétersbourg mu Burusiya.
Ivyo bisobanura ko ushobora gukoresha neza imisi nk'ingahe kugira ngo ugendere ico gisagara c'ivya kahise, maze ugataha n'ubwato mw'ijoro kugira ngo urareyo.
Mu gihe umuntu ashitse ku nkengera y'ikiyaga akoresheje ubwato bugendera ku mazi gusa, ntibikenewe ko aronka uruhusha rwo kwinjira muri ico gihugu (kuva mu 2009).
Mu nsiguro z'ubwato bumwe bumwe, harimwo igisagara ca Berlin mu Budagi. Nk'uko ubibona aho hejuru kw'ikarata, Berlin ntiri hafi y'ikiyaga na gato kandi kugendera ico gisagara ntibirimwo mu giciro c'ubwato.
Kugendera mu ndege birashobora kugutera ubwoba utarinze kuraba imyaka ufise canke kahise kawe, cane cane igihe utari bwigere ugenda mu ndege canke igihe woba warashikiwe n'ibintu bibabaje.
Ico si ikintu co guterwa isoni: ntaho gitandukaniye n'ubwoba hamwe n'ukwanka abandi bantu benshi bagira.
Ku bantu bamwebamwe, gutahura ingene indege ikora n'ibiriko biraba mu gihe iriko iragenda, birashobora kubafasha gutsinda ubwoba bw'uko batazi ibintu canke ko badashobora kubigenzura.
Amashirahamwe y'ubutumwa aronka amahera menshi mu gutanga ibintu mu buryo bunyaruka. Akenshi, umwanya urahambaye cane ku mpapuro z'ubudandaji, ku bidandazwa canke ku bihimba vyo gusubiriza mu gihe vyihutirwa.
Mu ngendo zimwe zimwe, amashirahamwe manini afise indege zayo bwite, ariko hari ingorane mu zindi ngendo n'amashirahamwe matomato.
Mu gihe baba barungitse ibintu bakoresheje indege itwara imizigo, mu ngendo zimwezimwe vyarashobora gufata imisi itari mike kugira barangize gupakurura no kwinjiza ibidandazwa mu gihugu.
Kubera amategeko y'ishirahamwe ry'indege, ntushobora kurungika ibintu ata ngenzi irimwo, utegerezwa rero gukoresha ako karyo.
Uburyo busanzwe bwo gufata indege mu kibanza ca mbere canke c'abadandaza ni ugutanga amahera y'umurengera (canke naho vyoba vyiza, urwego rwawe rubigukorere).
Ariko ntibirazimvye: ugereranije, ushobora kuriha amahera angana n'incuro zine y'amahera y'urugendo rw'abadandaza n'incuro 11 y'amahera y'urugendo rwa mbere!
Muri rusangi, si vyiza kurondera uturusho tw'intebe zo mu bwoko bwa "business" canke ubwambere ku ngendo z'indege zitaziguye ziva mu kibanza A zija mu kibanza B.
Amakompanyi y'indege arazi neza ko hari umugwi munini w'abagendesha indege bemera kuriha amahera menshi kugira ngo bagire uburenganzira bwo gufata ingendo mu buryo bunyaruka kandi bwiza.
Umurwa mukuru wa Moldaviya ni Chisinau. Ururimi rw'aho ni ikirumaniya, ariko ikirusiya kirakoreshwa cane.
Moldaviya ni repubulika igizwe n'abantu b'ubwoko butandukanye yabayemwo indyane zishingiye ku moko.
Mu 1994, iyo ntambara yatumye mu buseruko bwa Moldaviya havuka Republika yigenga ya Transnistria, ifise leta yayo n'ifaranga ryayo, ariko ikaba itemewe n'igihugu na kimwe co muri ONU.
Imigenderanire mu vy'ubutunzi yasubiye gutangura hagati y'ivyo bice bibiri vya Moldaviya, naho ibiganiro vya politike ata co vyavuyemwo.
Idini rikomeye muri Moldaviya ni idini rya gikirisitu ry'aba Orthodox.
Izmir n'igisagara ca gatatu mu bunini muri Turukiya, gifise abanyagihugu bashika hafi imiliyoni 3,7, ikivuko ca kabiri kinini inyuma ya Istanbul n'ikibanza ciza cane c'uruja n'uruza.
Izinga rya Simuruna ryahoze ari igisagara ca kera, ubu ni igisagara ca none, giteye imbere kandi kirimwo uruja n'uruza rw'ibidandazwa, kikaba kiri ku nkengera y'ikiyaga kinini gikikujwe n'imisozi.
Hagati y'amabarabara yagutse, inyubakwa zifise impande z'ibirahuri n'ibibanza vy'ubudandaji bigezweho, hari ibisenge vy'amatafari atukura, amasoko yo mu kinjana ca 18 n'imisigiti n'amasengero ya kera, ariko ikirere c'igisagara kimeze nk'ica Buraya bwo mu kiyaga Mediterane aho kuba nk'ica Turukiya ya kera.
Igisagara ca Haldarsvík kiraba izinga rya Eysturoy riri hafi yaco, kandi kirimwo urusengero rudasanzwe rufise imfuruka umunani.
Ku mva zimwe zimwe zo mu kigo c'isengero hari ibishusho vy'inuma bikozwe mu mabuye y'agaciro.
Birakwiye gufata isaha n'igice ugendagenda muri ico kigwati giteye igomwe.
Mu buraruko hari igisagara giteye igomwe kandi giteye igomwe citwa Sintra, gisanzwe kizwi cane n'abanyamahanga kuva aho Lord Byron avugiye ivyiza vyaco.
Ibisi y'ibarabara 403 iva i Scotturb yama ija i Sintra, igahagarara i Cabo da Roca.
No mu buraruko, nuze kugendera urusengero runini rwa Bikira Mariya rw'i Fátima, rwabereyemwo ivyo kubonekerwa kwa Mariya bizwi cane kw'isi yose.
