Ako karere kandi karimwo ubwoko bwinshi cane bw'ibikoko n'inyoni.
Hariyo ibikoko vy'imbonekarimwe, nk'idubu y'ibara ry'urwatsi rutoto, imfyisi, inkukuma, injangwe, injangwe zo mw'ishamba be n'ibikoko vyo mu bwoko bw'imvubu.
