Abagabo na bo nyene bategerezwa kwambara amapantalo ashika kw'ivi.
Urashobora no kuyikura mu bubiko buri ku bwinjiriro, ariko izo mpuzu ntizihora zimesurwa, ari co gituma ushobora kwumva ubuze amahoro mu kwambara izo mpuzu. Abagabo bose barangana!
Imfungurwa zo muri Majorque, cokimwe n'izo mu tundi turere two muri Mediterane, zishingiye ku mukate, imboga n'inyama (canecane iz'ingurube) kandi zikoresha amavuta y'imyelayo ahantu hose.
Imfungurwa zo ku mugoroba zisanzwe zikundwa na benshi, na canecane mu ci, ni "pa amb oli": umukate urimwo amavuta y'umwelayo, itomati be n'ikindi kintu cose kirimwo, nk'iforomaji, tuna n'ibindi.
